name: Fendu_Tisk
content:
Fendu Tisk was a Revwien male student of the Force who was affiliated with the Alliance to Restore the Republic during the Galactic Civil War against the Galactic Empire. He stood 2.3 meters tall and was skilled in dodging, starship piloting, and bargaining, and was knowledgeable about alien races, languages, and medicine. He carried a medpac and an alien memento.
Fendu Tisk was created for the Rebel Characters Adventure Set, a boxed set of metal miniatures released in 1989 by West End Games to be used with Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game. Tisk's character type was listed as "Alien Student of the Force" and his model came unpainted.
